description: Just Jackie’s Food Truck established in November 2012. JJ’s is serving new age comfort food to the greater Philadelphia area.Partners Jackie Borelli and Bonnie Offit have teamed together to produce fast, fresh, and healthy meals. With everything being homemade, the secret sauces take the sandwiches from good to great. From French onion soup and spicy chicken sandwich, to sumac chicken feta wrap and pulled pork tacos with sriracha aioli, JJ serves it all.Just Jackie’s has taken comfort food to the next level. When you bite into one of JJ’s sandwiches, such as the melted Brie with a homemade sweet onion jam and crispy granny smith apples, you’ll be transformed into another world. JJ’s main goal is to provide meals that pleasure your palate without emptying your wallet.Don’t be afraid to express an allergy or food concern, because JJ is here to accommodate and make your food experience friendly and satisfying.
name: Just Jackies Food truck
